1028
01:51:41,028 --> 01:51:43,780
It's time to come together.

1029
01:51:43,864 --> 01:51:49,285
What's important is not what's gone,
but what remains.

1030
01:51:49,370 --> 01:51:52,288
We still have
half the world's forests,

1031
01:51:52,373 --> 01:51:54,957
thousands of rivers,
lakes and glaciers...

1032
01:51:55,042 --> 01:51:57,126
and thousands of thriving species.

1033
01:51:57,211 --> 01:52:00,380
dd

1034
01:52:01,757 --> 01:52:05,551
We know that the solutions
are there today.

1035
01:52:05,636 --> 01:52:08,137
We all have the power to change.

1036
01:52:10,140 --> 01:52:12,809
So what are we waiting for?

